<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%= @tenant&.name || "CRM ISWO" %></title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
             background: #f5f7fb; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #1f2937; }
      .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
      .card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px;
              box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); overflow: hidden; }
      .header { padding: 24px; background: <%= @tenant&.brand_color || "#0f172a" %>;
                color: #ffffff; text-align: left; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
      .body { padding: 24px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px;
             background: <%= @tenant&.brand_color || "#0f172a" %>; color: #ffffff;
             text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
      .muted { color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; }
      .footer { padding: 16px 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;
                border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
      a { color: <%= @tenant&.brand_color || "#0f172a" %>; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="header">
          <h1><%= @tenant&.name || "CRM ISWO" %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <%= yield %>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
          Este correo fue enviado automáticamente por el CRM.
          Si tienes dudas, responde a este mensaje.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
